Package maltcms.commands.fragments.warp

Class Summary
ChromatogramWarp Deprecated.
ChromatogramWarp2 Use Objects of this class to apply an alignment, warping a source chromatogram to the time/scans of reference chromatogram.
PathWarp Instead of warping one time series to the time scale of another one, warp both to their common time, given by the steps of the alignment map.
RTGroupCorrectionWarp Use Objects of this class to apply an alignment, warping a source chromatogram to the time/scans of reference chromatogram.
